981685,182,33,2,5,1,35,3,Kathaṃ bahiddhāsamuṭṭhānaṃ ottappaṃ?
981686,182,33,6,33,1,192,21,"‘‘ Sace tvaṃ pāpakammaṃ karissasi, catūsu parisāsu garahappatto bhavissasi, tato taṃ sīlavanto sabrahmacārī vivajjissantī’’ ti paccavekkhitvā bahiddhāsamuṭṭhānaṃ ottappaṃ nissāya pāpakammaṃ na karoti. "
981687,182,33,34,37,1,33,3,Evaṃ bahiddhāsamuṭṭhānaṃ ottappaṃ. 
981688,182,34,2,6,1,23,3,Kathaṃ attādhipati hirī? 
981689,182,34,7,29,1,155,18,Idhekacco kulaputto attānaṃ adhipatiṃ jeṭṭhakaṃ katvā‘‘ mādisassa saddhāpabbajitassa bahussutassa dhutadharassa na yuttaṃ pāpakammaṃ kātun’’ ti pāpaṃ na karoti. 
981690,182,34,30,33,1,21,3,Evaṃ attādhipati hirī. 
981691,182,34,34,69,1,147,18,"Tenāha bhagavā‘‘ so attānaṃyeva adhipatiṃ karitvā akusalaṃ pajahati, kusalaṃ bhāveti, sāvajjaṃ pajahati, anavajjaṃ bhāveti, suddhaṃ attānaṃ pariharatī’’ ti( a. ni.3.40). "
981692,182,35,2,6,1,27,3,Kathaṃ lokādhipati ottappaṃ? 
981693,182,35,7,46,1,232,32,"Idhekacco kulaputto lokaṃ adhipatiṃ jeṭṭhakaṃ katvā‘‘ sace kho tvaṃ pāpakammaṃ kareyyāsi, sabrahmacārino tāva taṃ jānissanti, mahiddhikā mahānubhāvā loke ca samaṇabrāhmaṇā devatā ca, tasmā te na yuttaṃ pāpaṃ kātun’’ ti pāpakammaṃ na karoti. "
981694,182,35,47,48,1,7,1,Yathāha–
981695,182,35,49,65,1,127,13,"‘‘ mahā kho panāyaṃ lokasannivāso, mahantasmiṃ kho pana lokasannivāse santi samaṇabrāhmaṇā iddhimanto dibbacakkhukā paracittaviduno. "
981696,182,35,66,102,1,211,28,"Te dūratopi passanti, āsannāpi na dissanti, cetasāpi cittaṃ jānanti, tepi maṃ evaṃ jānissanti‘ passatha, bho, imaṃ kulaputtaṃ, saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito samāno vokiṇṇo viharati pāpakehi akusalehi dhammehī’ ti. "
981697,182,35,103,159,1,326,41,"Santi devatā iddhimantiniyo dibbacakkhukā paracittaviduniyo, tā dūratopi passanti, āsannāpi na dissanti, cetasāpi cittaṃ jānanti, tāpi maṃ jānissanti‘ passatha, bho, imaṃ kulaputtaṃ, saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito samāno vokiṇṇo viharati pāpakehi akusalehi dhammehī’ ti… pe… so lokaṃyeva adhipatiṃ karitvā akusalaṃ… pe… pariharatī’’ ti. "
