982856,182,251,2,7,1,20,2,( 14)4. Santhāravaggavaṇṇanā 
982857,182,252,2,25,1,165,19,152. Catutthassa paṭhame āmisassa ca dhammassa ca alābhena attano parassa ca antare sambhavantassa chiddassa vivarassa bhedassa santharaṇaṃ pidahanaṃ saṅgaṇhanaṃ santhāro. 
982858,182,252,26,34,1,69,8,Ayañhi lokasannivāso alabbhamānena āmisena dhammena cāti dvīhi chiddo. 
982859,182,252,35,54,1,134,17,"Tassa taṃ chiddaṃ yathā na paññāyati , evaṃ pīṭhassa viya paccattharaṇena āmisena dhammena ca santharaṇaṃ saṅgaṇhanaṃ santhāroti vuccati. "
982860,182,252,55,61,1,43,6,Ettha ca āmisena saṅgaho āmisasanthāro nāma. 
982861,182,252,62,74,1,108,11,Taṃ karontena mātāpitūnaṃ bhikkhugatikassa veyyāvaccakarassa rañño corānañca aggaṃ aggahetvāpi dātuṃ vaṭṭati. 
982862,182,252,75,86,1,77,10,"Āmasitvā dinnehi rājāno ca corā ca anatthampi karonti, jīvitakkhayampi pāpenti. "
982863,182,252,87,96,1,82,8,"Anāmasitvā dinnena attamanā honti, coranāgavatthuādīni cettha vatthūni kathetabbāni. "
982864,182,252,97,106,1,54,4,Tāni samantapāsādikāya vinayaṭṭhakathāyaṃ( pārā.185) vitthāritāni. 
982865,182,252,107,116,1,97,9,Sakkaccaṃ uddesadānaṃ pāḷivaṇṇanā dhammakathākathananti evaṃ dhammena saṅgaho dhammasanthāro nāma. 
