982869,182,255,2,7,1,21,2,( 15)5. Samāpattivaggavaṇṇanā 
982870,182,256,2,29,1,160,18,"164. Pañcamassa paṭhame‘‘ ito pubbe parikammaṃ pavattaṃ, ito paraṃ bhavaṅgaṃ majjhe samāpattī’’ ti evaṃ saha parikammena appanāparicchedappajānanā paññā samāpattikusalatā. "
982871,182,256,30,33,1,37,3,Vuṭṭhāne kusalabhāvo vuṭṭhānakusalatā. 
982872,182,256,34,39,1,60,5,Pageva vuṭṭhānaparicchedakañāṇanti evamettha attho daṭṭhabbo. 
982873,182,257,2,15,1,62,8,"165. Dutiye ujuno bhāvo ajjavaṃ, ajimhatā akuṭilatā avaṅkatāti attho. "
982874,182,257,16,25,1,19,2,Abhidhammepi( dha. sa.1346) vuttaṃ–
982875,182,257,26,31,1,20,3,‘‘ tattha katamo ajjavo? 
982876,182,257,32,44,1,62,9,"Yā ajjavatā ajimhatā akuṭilatā avaṅkatā, ayaṃ vuccati ajjavo’’ ti. "
982877,182,257,45,48,1,42,3,Anajjavañca ajjavappaṭikkhepena veditabbaṃ. 
982878,182,257,49,57,1,70,6,"Gomuttavaṅkatā, candalekhāvaṅkatā, naṅgalakoṭivaṅkatāti hi tayo anajjavā. "
982879,182,257,58,81,1,182,21,"Ekacco hi bhikkhu paṭhamavaye majjhima-pacchimavaye ca ekavīsatiyā anesanāsu chasu ca agocaresu carati, ayaṃ gomuttavaṅkatā nāma, ādito paṭṭhāya yāva pariyosānā paṭipattiyā vaṅkabhāvato. "
982880,182,257,82,105,1,188,18,"Eko paṭhamavaye pacchimavaye ca catupārisuddhisīlaṃ pūreti, lajjī kukkuccako sikkhākāmo hoti, majjhimavaye purimasadiso, ayaṃ candalekhāvaṅkatā nāma, paṭipattiyā majjhaṭṭhāne vaṅkabhāvāpattito. "
982881,182,257,106,126,1,176,16,"Eko paṭhamavayepi majjhimavayepi catupārisuddhisīlaṃ pūreti, lajjī kukkuccako sikkhākāmo hoti, pacchimavaye purimasadiso, ayaṃ naṅgalakoṭivaṅkatā nāma, pariyosāne vaṅkabhāvāpattito. "
982882,182,257,127,151,1,149,20,"Eko sabbampetaṃ vaṅkataṃ pahāya tīsu vayesu pesalo lajjī kukkuccako sikkhākāmo hoti, tassa yo so ujubhāvo, idaṃ ajjavaṃ nāma, sabbattha ujubhāvasiddhito. "
982883,182,258,2,12,1,41,6,Maddavan ti ettha‘‘ lajjavan’’ tipi paṭhanti. 
982884,182,258,13,16,1,19,3,Evaṃ panettha attho–
982885,182,258,17,22,1,21,3,‘‘ tattha katamo lajjavo? 
982886,182,258,23,43,1,137,17,"Yo hirīyati hirīyitabbena hirīyati pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ samāpattiyā, ayaṃ vuccati lajjavo’’ ti evaṃ vutto lajjibhāvo lajjavaṃ nāma. "
982887,182,258,44,59,1,81,11,"Idaṃ panettha nibbacanaṃ– lajjatīti lajjo, hirimā, tassa bhāvo lajjavaṃ, hirīti attho. "
982888,182,258,60,80,1,81,14,"Lajjā etassa atthīti lajjī yathā‘‘ mālī māyī’’ ti, tassa bhāvo lajjibhāvo, sā eva lajjā. "
982889,182,259,2,13,1,60,6,166. Tatiye {adhivāsanakhantī}ti ettha adhivāsanaṃ vuccati khamanaṃ. 
982890,182,259,14,30,1,107,12,Tañhi paresaṃ dukkaṭaṃ duruttañca paṭivirodhākaraṇena attano upari āropetvā vāsanato‘‘ adhivāsanan’’ ti vuccati. 
