982933,182,271,2,21,1,144,13,"176. Terasame {sīlavisuddhī}ti visuddhiṃ pāpetuṃ samatthaṃ sīlaṃ, cittavisuddhiādiuparivisuddhiyā paccayo bhavituṃ samatthaṃ visuddhasīlanti vuttaṃ hoti. "
