982939,182,272,2,18,1,172,14,"{Diṭṭhivisuddhī}ti visuddhiṃ pāpetuṃ samatthaṃ dassanañāṇaṃ dassanavisuddhi, paramatthavisuddhiṃ nibbānañca pāpetuṃ upanetuṃ samatthaṃ kammassakatañāṇādi sammādassananti attho. "
982940,182,272,19,32,1,58,7,Tenāha‘‘ visuddhisampāpikā… pe… pañcavidhāpi vā sammādiṭṭhī’’ ti. 
982941,182,272,33,44,1,130,9,Etthāpi {visuddhisampāpikā}ti ñāṇadassanavisuddhiyā dassananibbānasaṅkhātāya paramatthavisuddhiyā ca sampāpikāti evamattho daṭṭhabbo. 
982942,182,272,45,59,1,47,5,Abhidhamme( dha. sa.1373) panāyaṃ‘‘ tattha katamā diṭṭhivisuddhi? 
982943,182,272,60,76,1,106,11,"Kammassakatañāṇaṃ, saccānulomikaṃ ñāṇaṃ, maggassa maggasamaṅgissa ñāṇaṃ, phalasamaṅgissa ñāṇan’’ ti evaṃ vuttaṃ. "
982944,182,273,2,19,1,132,16,"Ettha ca idaṃ akusalakammaṃ no sakaṃ, idaṃ pana kammaṃ sakanti evaṃ byatirekato anvayato ca kammassakatajānanañāṇaṃ kammassakatañāṇaṃ. "
982945,182,273,20,35,1,129,14,"Tividhaduccaritañhi attanā katampi parena katampi no sakakammaṃ nāma hoti atthabhañjanato, sucaritaṃ sakakammaṃ nāma atthajananato. "
982946,182,273,36,47,1,104,10,"Vipassanāñāṇaṃ pana vacīsaccañca anulometi, paramatthasaccañca na vilometīti saccānulomikañāṇan ti vuttaṃ. "
982947,182,273,48,75,1,214,21,"Vipassanāñāṇañhi lakkhaṇāni paṭivijjhanatthaṃ ārambhakāle ‘‘ aniccaṃ dukkhaṃ anattā’’ ti pavattaṃ vacīsaccañca anulometi, tatheva paṭivijjhanato paramatthasaccaṃ nibbānañca na vilometi na virādheti ekanteneva sampāpanato. "
982948,182,274,2,11,1,56,4,177. Cuddasame {diṭṭhivisuddhī}ti paṭhamamaggasammādiṭṭhi vuttā. 
982949,182,274,12,18,1,55,6,Yathādiṭṭhissa ca padhānan ti taṃsampayuttameva vīriyaṃ. 
982950,182,274,19,37,1,69,5,Teneva dīghanikāyaṭṭhakathāyaṃ( dī. ni. aṭṭha.3.304)‘‘ diṭṭhivisuddhīti ñāṇadassanaṃ kathitaṃ. 
982951,182,274,38,47,1,64,7,Yathādiṭṭhissa ca padhānanti taṃsampayuttameva vīriyan’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
982952,182,274,48,54,1,44,6,Ettha hi ñāṇadassanan ti ñāṇabhūtaṃ dassanaṃ. 
982953,182,274,55,58,1,25,3,Tena dassanamaggaṃ vadati. 
982954,182,274,59,63,1,61,4,Taṃsampayuttameva vīriyan ti paṭhamamaggasampayuttavīriyamāha. 
982955,182,274,64,69,1,47,4,Apica {diṭṭhivisuddhī}ti sabbāpi maggasammādiṭṭhi. 
982956,182,274,70,76,1,55,6,Yathādiṭṭhissa ca padhānan ti taṃsampayuttameva vīriyaṃ. 
982957,182,274,77,92,1,112,10,"Teneva dīghanikāyaṭṭhakathāyaṃ‘‘ apica purimapadena catumaggañāṇaṃ, pacchimapadena taṃsampayuttaṃ vīriyan’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
982958,182,275,2,10,1,77,7,Atha vā {diṭṭhīvisuddhī}ti kammassakatañāṇādisaṅkhātā sabbāpi sammādiṭṭhi vuttā. 
982959,182,275,11,22,1,71,9,Yathādiṭṭhissa ca padhānan ti yo cetasiko vīriyārambho… pe… sammāvāyāmoti. 
982960,182,275,23,26,1,21,3,Ayameva pāḷiyā sameti. 
982961,182,275,27,43,1,91,12,Abhidhamme hi‘‘ diṭṭhivisuddhi kho panāti yā paññā pajānanā… pe… amoho dhammavicayo sammādiṭṭhi. 
982962,182,275,44,60,1,94,12,Yathādiṭṭhissa ca padhānanti yo cetasiko vīriyārambho… pe… sammāvāyāmo’’ ti evamayaṃ duko vibhatto. 
982963,182,275,61,83,1,118,11,Teneva abhidhammaṭṭhakathāyaṃ( dha. sa. aṭṭha.1374)‘‘ yā paññā pajānanātiādīhi heṭṭhā vuttāni kammassakatañāṇādīneva cattāri ñāṇāni vibhattāni.
982964,182,275,84,105,1,133,15,"‘ Yo cetasiko vīriyārambho’ tiādīhi padehi niddiṭṭhaṃ vīriyaṃ gahitaṃ paññāya lokiyaṭṭhāne lokiyaṃ, lokuttaraṭṭhāne lokuttaran’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
982965,182,276,2,20,1,163,13,"Idhāpi visuddhisampāpikā catumaggasammādiṭṭhi, pañcavidhāpi vā sammādiṭṭhi diṭṭhivisuddhīti adhippāyena‘‘ diṭṭhivisuddhīti visuddhisampāpikā sammādiṭṭhiyevā’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
982966,182,276,21,39,1,137,14,Heṭṭhimamaggasampayuttaṃ vīriyan ti idaṃ pana‘‘ yathādiṭṭhissa ca padhānanti paṭhamamaggasampayuttaṃ vīriyanti vuttan’’ ti adhippāyena vadati. 
982967,182,276,40,49,1,106,9,Ettha ca taṃtaṃbhāṇakānaṃ matabhedenāyaṃ vaṇṇanābhedoti na aṭṭhakathāvacanānaṃ aññamaññavirodho saṅkitabbo. 
982968,182,276,50,68,1,127,14,Atha yathādiṭṭhissa ca padhānanti heṭṭhimamaggasampayuttameva vīriyaṃ kasmā vuttanti āha‘‘ tañhi tassā diṭṭhiyā anurūpattā’’ tiādi. 
982969,182,276,69,75,1,58,5,Tattha tassā {diṭṭhiyā}ti heṭṭhimamaggasampayuttāya diṭṭhiyā. 
