986150,182,957,2,10,1,33,3,126. Tatiye {sambahulā}ti pañcasatamattā. 
986151,182,957,11,39,1,244,28,Pañcasatā kira brāhmaṇā tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū aparabhāge bhagavato dhammadesanaṃ sutvā kāmesu ādīnavaṃ nekkhamme ca ānisaṃsaṃ passamānā bhagavato santike pabbajitvā na cirasseva sabbaṃ buddhavacanaṃ uggaṇhitvā pariyattiṃ nissāya mānaṃ uppādesuṃ–
986152,182,957,40,52,1,55,9,"‘‘ yaṃ yaṃ bhagavā katheti, taṃ taṃ mayaṃ khippameva jānāma. "
986153,182,957,53,94,1,271,35,"Bhagavā hi itthiliṅgādīni tīṇi liṅgāni, nāmādīni cattāri padāni, paṭhamādayo satta vibhattiyo muñcitvā na kiñci katheti, evaṃ kathite ca amhākaṃ gaṇṭhipadaṃ nāma natthī’’ ti, te bhagavati agāravā hutvā tato paṭṭhāya bhagavato upaṭṭhānampi dhammassavanampi abhiṇhaṃ na gacchanti. "
986154,182,957,95,112,1,85,11,Te sandhāya vuttaṃ‘‘ sambahulā kira brāhmaṇapabbajitā… pe… dhammassavanaṃ na gacchantī’’ ti. 
