986163,182,958,64,66,1,23,2,Tesaṃ mānabhañjanatthaṃ. 
986164,182,958,67,109,1,232,25,Bhagavā hi‘‘ abhabbā ime imaṃ mānakhilaṃ anupahacca maggaṃ vā phalaṃ vā sacchikātun’’ ti tesaṃ sutapariyattiṃ nissāya uppannaṃ aṭṭhuppattiṃ katvā desanākusalo mānabhañjanatthaṃ‘‘ sabbadhammamūlapariyāyan’’ tiādinā mūlapariyāyasuttaṃ( ma. ni.1.1) abhāsi. 
986165,182,959,2,20,1,136,12,Sammāsambuddho ‘‘ mayhaṃ kathā niyyātī’’ ti mukhasampattameva kathetīti {cintayiṃsū}ti idaṃ aṅguttarabhāṇakānaṃ vaḷañjanakatantinīhārena vuttaṃ. 
986166,182,959,21,95,1,477,61,"Majjhimabhāṇakā pana evaṃ vadanti– evaṃ mānabhañjanatthaṃ desitañca pana taṃ suttaṃ sutvā te bhikkhū‘‘ taṃyeva kira pathaviṃ diṭṭhigatiko sañjānāti, sekhopi arahāpi tathāgatopi abhijānāti, ki nāmidaṃ kathaṃ nāmidan’’ ti cintentā‘‘ pubbe mayaṃ bhagavatā kathitaṃ yaṃkiñci khippameva jānāma, idāni panimassa mūlapariyāyassa antaṃ vā koṭiṃ vā na jānāma na passāma, aho buddhā nāma appameyyā atulā’’ ti uddhatadāṭhā viya sappā nimmadā hutvā buddhūpaṭṭhānañca dhammassavanañca sakkaccaṃ agamaṃsu. "
986167,182,959,96,120,1,186,19,"Tena samayena dhammasabhāyaṃ sannisinnā bhikkhū‘‘ aho buddhānaṃ ānubhāvo, te nāmabrāhmaṇapabbajitā tathā mānamadamattā bhagavatā mūlapariyāyadesanāya nihatamānā katā’’ ti kathaṃ samuṭṭhāpesuṃ. "
986168,182,959,121,173,1,386,40,"Taṃ sutvā bhagavā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, idāneva, pubbepi ahaṃ evaṃ ime mānapaggahitasīse carante nihatamāne akāsin’’ ti vatvā atītaṃ āharanto‘‘ bhūtapubbaṃ, bhikkhave, aññataro disāpāmokkho brāhmaṇo bārāṇasiyaṃ paṭivasati tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū sanighaṇṭukeṭubhānaṃ sākkharappabhedānaṃ itihāsapañcamānaṃ padako veyyākaraṇo lokāyatamahāpurisalakkhaṇesu anavayo, so pañcamattāni māṇavakasatāni mante vāceti. "
986169,182,959,174,187,1,87,10,"Paṇḍitamāṇavakā bahuñca gaṇhanti lahuñca, suṭṭhu ca upadhārentī’’ tiādinā jātakaṃ kathesi. "
