986685,182,1085,2,13,1,76,6,12. Dutiye {sampannasīlā}ti ettha tividhaṃ sampannaṃ paripuṇṇasamaṅgimadhuravasena. 
986686,182,1085,14,15,1,6,1,Tattha–
986687,182,1086,2,11,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Sampannaṃ sālikedāraṃ, suvā bhuñjanti kosiya; "
986688,182,1087,2,22,1,43,7,"Paṭivedemi te brahme, na ne vāretumussahe’’ ti.( jā.1.14.1)– "
986689,182,1088,2,6,1,28,3,Idaṃ paripuṇṇasampannaṃ nāma.
986690,182,1088,7,30,1,124,14,‘‘ Iminā pātimokkhasaṃvarena upeto hoti samupeto upāgato samupāgato upapanno sampanno samannāgato’’ ti( vibha.511) idaṃ samaṅgisampannaṃ nāma.
986691,182,1088,31,57,1,126,13,"‘‘ Imissā, bhante, mahāpathaviyā heṭṭhimatalaṃ sampannaṃ, seyyathāpi khuddamadhuṃ anīlakaṃ, evamassādan’’ ti( pārā.17) idaṃ madhurasampannaṃ nāma. "
986692,182,1088,58,70,1,80,8,Idha paripuṇṇasampannavasena atthaṃ dassento‘‘ sampannasīlāti paripuṇṇasīlā’’ ti āha. 
986693,182,1088,71,85,1,136,12,"Samaṅgisampannavasenapi attho yujjatiyeva, tasmā {sampannasīlā}ti paripuṇṇasīlā hutvātipi sīlasamaṅgino hutvātipi evamettha attho daṭṭhabbo. "
986694,182,1088,86,96,1,120,9,"Tattha sīlassa anavasesasamādānena akhaṇḍādibhāvappattiyā paripuṇṇasīlā, samādānato paṭṭhāya avicchindanato sīlasamaṅgino. "
986695,182,1088,97,110,1,153,12,"Samādānavato hi accantavirodhidhammānuppattiyā sīlasamaṅgitā veditabbā, cetanādīnaṃ pana sīlanalakkhaṇānaṃ dhammānaṃ pavattilakkhaṇena vattabbameva natthi. "
986696,182,1089,2,18,1,117,12,Tattha ‘‘ paripuṇṇasīlā’’ ti iminā atthena khettadosavigamena khettapāripūrī viya sīladosavigamena sīlapāripūrī vuttā hoti. 
986697,182,1089,19,32,1,104,10,"Yathā hi khettaṃ bījakhaṇḍaṃ, vappakhaṇḍaṃ, udakakhaṇḍaṃ, ūsakhaṇḍanti catudosasamannāgataṃ aparipūraṃ hoti. "
986698,182,1089,33,61,1,167,24,"Tattha bījakhaṇḍaṃ nāma yattha antarantarā bījāni khaṇḍāni vā pūtīni vā honti, tāni yattha patanti, tattha sassaṃ na uṭṭheti, khettaṃ khaṇḍaṃ hoti, aparipūraṃ hotīti attho. "
986699,182,1089,62,70,1,68,8,Vappakhaṇḍaṃ nāma yattha akusalo bījāni vapanto antarantarā nipāteti. 
986700,182,1089,71,80,1,55,8,"Evañhi sabbattha sassaṃ na uṭṭheti, khettaṃ khaṇḍaṃ hoti. "
986701,182,1089,81,93,1,68,11,"Udakakhaṇḍaṃ nāma yattha katthaci udakaṃ atibahuṃ vā hoti, na vā hoti. "
986702,182,1089,94,103,1,51,8,"Tatrāpi hi sassāni na uṭṭhenti, khettaṃ khaṇḍaṃ hoti. "
986703,182,1089,104,122,1,130,17,"Ūsakhaṇḍaṃ nāma yattha kassako kismiñci padese naṅgalena bhūmiṃ cattāro pañca vāre kasanto atigambhīraṃ karoti, tato ūsaṃ uppajjati. "
986704,182,1089,123,140,1,103,15,"Tatrāpi hi sassaṃ na uṭṭheti, khettaṃ khaṇḍaṃ hoti, tādisañca khettaṃ na mahapphalaṃ hoti na mahānisaṃsaṃ. "
986705,182,1089,141,146,1,37,5,Tatrāpi bahumpi vapitvā appaṃ labhati. 
986706,182,1089,147,161,1,107,13,"Imesaṃ pana catunnaṃ dosānaṃ vigamā khettaṃ paripuṇṇaṃ hoti, tādisañca khettaṃ mahapphalaṃ hoti mahānisaṃsaṃ. "
986707,182,1089,162,183,1,137,16,"Evameva khaṇḍaṃ, chiddaṃ, sabalaṃ, kammāsanti catudosasamannāgataṃ sīlaṃ aparipūraṃ hoti, tādisañca sīlaṃ na mahapphalaṃ hoti na mahānisaṃsaṃ. "
