989007,182,1650,24,48,1,190,16,"‘‘ Tejosaṃvaṭṭo, āposaṃvaṭṭo, vāyosaṃvaṭṭoti evaṃ saṃvaṭṭasīmānukkamena saṃvaṭṭesu vattabbesu tathā avatvā āposaṃvaṭṭo, tejosaṃvaṭṭo, vāyosaṃvaṭṭoti vacanaṃ saṃvaṭṭamahābhūtadesanānupubbiyā’’ ti keci."
