989041,182,1661,2,4,1,21,2,1 . Saṃkhittasuttavaṇṇanā 
989042,182,1662,2,17,1,87,8,161. Dutiyassa paṭhame dukkhāpaṭipadā {dandhābhiññā}tiādīsu pāḷiyā āgatanayena attho veditabbo. 
989043,182,1662,18,20,1,8,2,Tathā hi–
989044,182,1663,2,9,1,47,6,‘ ‘ Tattha katamā dukkhapaṭipadā dandhābhiññā paññā? 
989045,182,1663,10,34,1,182,21,"Kicchena kasirena samādhiṃ uppādentassa dandhaṃ taṃ ṭhānaṃ abhijānantassa yā uppajjati paññā pajānanā… pe… amoho dhammavicayo sammādiṭṭhi, ayaṃ vuccati dukkhapaṭipadā dandhābhiññā paññā. "
989046,182,1663,35,40,1,47,5,Tattha katamā dukkhapaṭipadā khippābhiññā paññā? 
989047,182,1663,41,63,1,163,19,"Kicchena kasirena samādhiṃ uppādentassa khippaṃ taṃ ṭhānaṃ abhijānantassa yā uppajjati paññā pajānanā… pe… sammādiṭṭhi, ayaṃ vuccati dukkhapaṭipadā khippābhiññā paññā. "
989048,182,1663,64,69,1,46,5,Tattha katamā sukhapaṭipadā dandhābhiññā paññā? 
989049,182,1663,70,92,1,164,19,"Akicchena akasirena samādhiṃ uppādentassa dandhaṃ taṃ ṭhānaṃ abhijānantassa yā uppajjati paññā pajānanā… pe… sammādiṭṭhi, ayaṃ vuccati sukhapaṭipadā dandhābhiññā paññā. "
989050,182,1663,93,98,1,46,5,Tattha katamā sukhapaṭipadā khippābhiññā paññā? 
989051,182,1663,99,132,1,182,22,"Akicchena akasirena samādhiṃ uppādentassa khippaṃ taṃ ṭhānaṃ abhijānantassa yā uppajjati paññā pajānanā… pe… sammādiṭṭhi, ayaṃ vuccati sukhapaṭipadā khippābhiññā paññā’’ ti( vibha.801)– ayamettha pāḷi. "
989052,182,1664,2,19,1,175,16,Tattha kicchena kasirena samādhiṃ {uppādentassā}ti pubbabhāge āgamanakāle kicchena kasirena dukkhena sasaṅkhārena sappayogena kilese vikkhambhetvā lokuttarasamādhiṃ uppādentassa. 
989053,182,1664,20,40,1,197,18,"Dandhaṃ taṃ ṭhānaṃ {abhijānantassā}ti vikkhambhitesu kilesesu vipassanāparivāse ciraṃ vasitvā taṃ lokuttarasamādhisaṅkhātaṃ ṭhānaṃ dandhaṃ saṇikaṃ abhijānantassa paṭivijjhantassa, pāpuṇantassāti attho. "
989054,182,1664,41,71,1,218,22,"Ayaṃ {vuccatī}ti yā esā evaṃ uppajjati, ayaṃ kilesavikkhambhanappaṭipadāya dukkhattā, vipassanāparivāsapaññāya ca dandhattā maggakāle ekacittakkhaṇe uppannāpi paññā āgamanavasena‘‘ dukkhapaṭipadā dandhābhiññā nāmā’’ ti vuccati. "
