989129,182,1689,2,16,1,82,8,170. Dasame samathapubbaṅgamaṃ vipassanaṃ {bhāvetī}ti idaṃ samathayānikassa vasena vuttaṃ. 
989130,182,1689,17,28,1,73,10,"So hi paṭhamaṃ upacārasamādhiṃ vā appanāsamādhiṃ vā uppādeti, ayaṃ samatho. "
989131,182,1689,29,46,1,106,14,"So tañca taṃsampayutte ca dhamme aniccādīhi vipassati, ayaṃ vipassanā, iti paṭhamaṃ samatho, pacchā vipassanā. "
