989176,182,1699,16,38,1,160,18,Te kira puññavisesādhigatena mahantena attano sirivibhavena nakkhattaṃ kīḷantā tāya sampattiyā mahantatāya‘‘ āhāraṃ paribhuñjimhā na paribhuñjimhā’’ tipi na jānanti. 
